high_descs: Turn around and go to the front of the sink.
Pick up the chef's knife on the edge of the sink.
Turn left from the current position.
Move forward a little to the counter on the right of the refrigerator.
Slice the tomato on the counter.
Turn right and place the knife on the sink's edge.
Turn left towards the tomato.
Pick up a slice of tomato.
Turn around to move to the front of the sink.
Heat the tomato in the microwave above the sink and take it out.
Turn right and go to the golden trash can on the other side of the room.
Place the tomato in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Throw out a heated slice of tomato.

high_descs: Turn to the left and walk over to face the sink.
Pick up the knife on the edge of the sink.
Turn to the left and face the tomato on the counter.
Cut the tomato on the counter into slices.
Turn to the right to face the sink.
Place the knife on the edge of the sink.
Turn to the left to face the tomato on the counter.
Pick up a slice of the tomato on the counter.
Turn right and face the microwave above the sink.
Heat the tomato slice and remove it from the microwave.
Turn right and walk forward to face the trash can.
Place the tomato slice in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: To heat a tomato slice and place it in the trash can.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the sink.
Pick up a knife from the counter in front of the sink.
Turn left and go to the tomato on the counter.
Slice the tomato on the counter.
Go back to the sink.
Set the knife back down on the counter in front of the sink.
Go back to the tomato.
Pick up a slice from the tomato on the counter.
Turn around and walk to the microwave.
Put the tomato slice in the microwave and heat it.
Turn right and walk to the trash can.
Put the tomato slice in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated slice of tomato in the trash can.
